53:32.120 --> 53:33.360
We don't retire.

53:34.320 --> 53:35.321
We don't forget.

53:36.360 --> 53:39.523
There is a man coming from the
Middle East. An important man.

53:39.600 --> 53:42.126
He lands next week.
You'll go and meet him.

53:42.560 --> 53:45.245
You'll do as he asks.
But he needs your assistance.

53:45.640 --> 53:47.290
This is a foreign country to him.

53:50.480 --> 53:52.005
You'll need another man.

53:52.920 --> 53:53.967
You have someone?

53:54.040 --> 53:55.963
 Yeah, Yussif.
Good.

53:57.120 --> 54:00.602
You're going to help
our friend with Sergeant Conlon.

54:13.760 --> 54:15.125
Ash raf?

54:33.920 --> 54:35.365
Peaceful streets.

55:07.560 --> 55:08.925
lngleezee.

55:10.120 --> 55:11.326
What?

55:15.120 --> 55:16.610
Englishman.

56:00.320 --> 56:02.687
He gets up at 8:00AM,
goes to the barn,

56:02.760 --> 56:05.366
cleans it for an hour
and then goes to the stables.

56:05.440 --> 56:06.601
Who lives with him?

56:06.720 --> 56:08.404
- Nobody.
- No wife?

56:08.920 --> 56:09.921
No.

56:11.400 --> 56:14.006
When he comes out of his house,
follow him into the barn.

56:14.520 --> 56:15.726
Show him the gun.

56:16.880 --> 56:20.362
We come out, we beat him,
tie him, take him.

56:21.040 --> 56:23.646
You do everything like I tell you to,
you understand?

56:26.080 --> 56:27.889
A knife for you.

56:30.280 --> 56:31.486
No fork.

58:16.800 --> 58:18.325
Go and see what is happening.

01:00:41.480 --> 01:00:44.245
I'm going to cut
your head off like a pig's.

01:01:03.720 --> 01:01:05.802
- Anyone else here?
- No one.

01:01:08.960 --> 01:01:12.328
Put him in the van.
Put your dead friend there, too.

01:02:23.960 --> 01:02:25.291
Turn the camera on.

01:02:51.120 --> 01:02:52.963
(Man on radio)
Some breaking news for you now.

01:02:53.040 --> 01:02:56.044
A Mr Glenn Conlon
has been reported missing.

01:02:56.120 --> 01:02:59.602
Mr Conlon was a banker and
a former private in the Army Reserves.

01:03:00.480 --> 01:03:02.289
His sister, Rebecca Conlon,

01:03:02.360 --> 01:03:05.728
and her 8-month-old daughter
were found brutally murdered

01:03:05.840 --> 01:03:07.763
at his farm in Hertfordshire.

01:03:07.840 --> 01:03:09.842
The police have little to go on...

01:03:19.960 --> 01:03:21.644
There is anger in you.

01:03:23.440 --> 01:03:24.965
Makes no sense.

01:03:26.320 --> 01:03:28.004
Why are you helping us?

01:03:39.520 --> 01:03:43.366
You're angry with me about
the woman, the baby.

01:03:44.160 --> 01:03:48.688
Do you think he cared for the families
of the men he tortured and killed?

01:03:52.200 --> 01:03:56.330
You're confused in the head. Majnoon.

01:04:00.960 --> 01:04:02.200
Take it.

01:04:15.920 --> 01:04:18.241
These pigs kill our people

01:04:18.320 --> 01:04:22.928
all over the world
and you feel for them?

01:04:24.160 --> 01:04:25.491
What's the matter with you?

01:04:26.240 --> 01:04:27.651
Be a man!

01:04:36.880 --> 01:04:38.882
The woman saw my face.

01:04:40.040 --> 01:04:41.246
The baby.

01:04:49.720 --> 01:04:51.529
You're not one of us.

01:04:54.000 --> 01:04:56.765
You haven't suffered like we have.

01:05:01.080 --> 01:05:02.684
This is your country.

01:05:28.720 --> 01:05:31.121
Well, I am sorry about your friend,
you know.

01:05:31.200 --> 01:05:35.410
But he was taken doing God's will.

01:05:35.800 --> 01:05:37.689
- A true martyr.
- And that soldier?

01:05:39.040 --> 01:05:40.451
I mean, he was just a reserve.

01:05:42.560 --> 01:05:43.925
My friend.

01:05:44.000 --> 01:05:47.766
Do you think they would publicise
the fact that he was a torturer?

01:05:47.840 --> 01:05:49.808
And what about the woman
and the baby, huh?

01:05:49.880 --> 01:05:51.689
Collateral damage.

01:05:51.760 --> 01:05:55.287
Who invented that phrase? That...
Enough of this!

01:05:57.360 --> 01:05:59.408
You know you can't stay
in this country, huh?

01:06:00.760 --> 01:06:03.764
Too dangerous. One door closes.

01:06:04.520 --> 01:06:05.851
Another opens.

01:06:07.480 --> 01:06:10.290
Before our colleague left,
he said you were a capable man.

01:06:10.360 --> 01:06:13.045
But that you... You know, you need

01:06:13.120 --> 01:06:18.365
experience to see what
these pigs do to your people.

01:06:18.440 --> 01:06:19.441
Hmm?

01:06:21.080 --> 01:06:22.684
I think he was right.

01:06:25.640 --> 01:06:26.971
Afghanistan.

01:06:29.800 --> 01:06:33.282
You'll go there, with a new identity,
to our friends.

01:06:33.360 --> 01:06:36.807
Be taught useful things,
then you'll come back.

01:06:36.880 --> 01:06:38.211
And if you don't return...

01:06:39.840 --> 01:06:45.051
then your prize will be more than
anything any one of us could wish for.

01:06:46.720 --> 01:06:47.960
Paradise.

01:06:51.200 --> 01:06:53.123
It's what you wanted, yes?

01:06:59.080 --> 01:07:01.401
An unidentified,
deceased male was found

01:07:01.480 --> 01:07:04.768
horrifically burnt in an abandoned
warehouse in East London.

01:07:05.360 --> 01:07:09.046
The body was so disfigured
no details of him are available.

01:07:09.520 --> 01:07:11.602
The location was
a known drugs factory

01:07:11.680 --> 01:07:14.251
and haunt of local gangs and dealers.

01:07:14.320 --> 01:07:15.651
- Police are treating...

01:07:17.280 --> 01:07:19.567
There's nothing we could have done.
We were doing our job.

01:07:23.760 --> 01:07:25.569
Our job is to do what's right.

01:07:31.880 --> 01:07:33.291
What did she mean?

01:07:36.160 --> 01:07:38.970
She said something about you.
What was she talking about?

01:07:43.680 --> 01:07:46.365
My wife was killed in the bombings
a few years back.

01:07:50.240 --> 01:07:51.571
I'm sorry.

01:07:54.760 --> 01:07:56.808
She'd have been 34 this year.

01:07:59.320 --> 01:08:04.008
She had nothing to do with all...
With all this, you know?

01:08:05.880 --> 01:08:07.848
Some days...

01:08:09.680 --> 01:08:12.604
Yeah, some days, I...

01:08:18.560 --> 01:08:19.845
That thing still in there?

01:08:20.920 --> 01:08:22.046
What?

01:08:42.160 --> 01:08:43.649
How do you turn it off?

01:08:43.720 --> 01:08:45.609
You turn it that way. No.

01:08:46.200 --> 01:08:47.361
That way.

01:08:47.439 --> 01:08:48.885
The other way.

01:08:49.560 --> 01:08:51.288
- The other way. Yeah.

01:09:09.319 --> 01:09:10.560
You OK?

01:09:10.640 --> 01:09:12.005
Fine.

01:09:19.399 --> 01:09:21.084
I remember this.

01:09:21.720 --> 01:09:22.960
It's embarrassing.

01:09:28.600 --> 01:09:30.488
Look, I'm sorry about what happened.

01:09:33.000 --> 01:09:35.401
About the way I acted back then.
If I could change it, I would.

01:09:38.040 --> 01:09:39.609
Is everything all right with you, Kate?

01:09:39.800 --> 01:09:43.167
- With your life?
- It's fine.

01:09:45.840 --> 01:09:49.002
It's not as easy as it used to be,
but don't have to talk about that now.

01:09:50.640 --> 01:09:52.961
We just... We slipped away.

01:09:57.680 --> 01:09:59.887
I have never stopped
thinking about you, Kate.

01:10:00.880 --> 01:10:02.723
You have to know that.

01:10:17.200 --> 01:10:20.090
Look, if you have things to do,
we could just meet this afternoon.

01:10:21.680 --> 01:10:23.284
I know this pub.

01:10:25.600 --> 01:10:27.011
I'd like to.

01:10:37.360 --> 01:10:38.725
Where have you been?

01:10:42.920 --> 01:10:45.241
Paul was meant to go ahead last night.

01:10:46.120 --> 01:10:47.485
He's vanished.

01:10:51.920 --> 01:10:54.127
- Were you followed?
- No.

01:10:54.200 --> 01:10:55.645
- Are you sure?
- Yeah.

01:10:57.240 --> 01:10:59.242
We have to change our plans.

01:11:00.400 --> 01:11:02.880
You have to make contact
with the third man and help him.

01:11:03.200 --> 01:11:08.889
- You stay with him. I'll be in touch.
- When is he due to go ahead?

01:11:09.440 --> 01:11:10.726
Tomorrow.

01:11:12.480 --> 01:11:13.766
What's the matter with you?

01:11:16.600 --> 01:11:20.321
It isn't time to be weak and emotional.
We have no time for emotions now.

01:11:22.320 --> 01:11:24.527
Especially when your brothers
and sisters are suffering.

01:11:54.120 --> 01:11:55.610
You know who I am, yeah?

01:11:56.240 --> 01:11:58.322
- Yeah.
- Is there anything else?

01:11:58.400 --> 01:12:00.562
- Any papers? Receipts?
- No.

01:12:01.840 --> 01:12:03.444
OK, use this.

01:12:05.200 --> 01:12:06.531
I'm going to go first.

01:12:06.720 --> 01:12:09.610
You wait here for a few minutes
and then follow me, OK?

01:12:12.200 --> 01:12:13.201
You stay calm.

01:12:45.600 --> 01:12:47.568
Have a look round, Mark.
Check round the corner.

01:12:47.640 --> 01:12:49.165
Have a look up there.

01:12:50.440 --> 01:12:52.090
It's him!

01:13:03.520 --> 01:13:04.931
Fuck!

01:13:40.120 --> 01:13:42.327
- We got him.
I heard.

01:13:42.400 --> 01:13:43.925
There was someone there watching.

01:13:44.000 --> 01:13:45.650
- Who?
- I don't know.

01:13:45.720 --> 01:13:47.688
Somebody across the road.
He got away on a bike.

01:13:47.760 --> 01:13:49.524
He's connected.

01:13:49.600 --> 01:13:53.764
Get the CCTV footage.
Should be a clear shot of him.

01:13:53.880 --> 01:13:55.723
There are two rooms
at the Glassmore Hotel

01:13:55.800 --> 01:13:57.404
booked in the name
of Michael and John Smith.

01:13:57.480 --> 01:14:00.086
Check in.
I'll be there when I have something.

01:14:00.160 --> 01:14:03.448
One more thing. There is a team
on us, our people. Watch yourselves.

01:14:05.160 --> 01:14:06.525
Our people? Why?

01:14:07.400 --> 01:14:09.607
What we are doing is not
standard. Make sure that...

01:14:13.160 --> 01:14:14.605
Where the fuck's she gone?

01:14:35.600 --> 01:14:37.011
Hey-

01:14:40.680 --> 01:14:42.205
You look tired.

01:14:42.280 --> 01:14:43.691
I'm fine.

01:14:44.880 --> 01:14:47.121
It was a nightmare getting
here with all the madness.

01:14:47.240 --> 01:14:48.241
What?

01:14:48.320 --> 01:14:50.448
There was a bomb scare
on the train coming here.

01:14:51.680 --> 01:14:52.727
Scared shitless.

01:14:54.520 --> 01:14:57.922
Bunch of murdering maniacs.
Hope they kill the lot of them.

01:15:00.680 --> 01:15:03.809
You know when I said I didn't think
about those days at uni any more?

01:15:04.520 --> 01:15:06.329
- Yeah.
- I was lying.

01:15:07.920 --> 01:15:08.921
I know.

01:15:12.120 --> 01:15:14.248
You know, I thought I saw you
once a few years ago.

01:15:15.120 --> 01:15:17.202
I just lost you in the crowd.

01:15:19.160 --> 01:15:21.401
Well, I'm not going anywhere.

01:15:25.240 --> 01:15:28.164
Especially since it's your round.

01:15:36.960 --> 01:15:39.167
Can I get a red wine
and orange juice, please?

01:15:39.240 --> 01:15:40.571
No problem at all.

01:15:45.880 --> 01:15:48.406
There you go. That's £5 exactly.

01:15:52.320 --> 01:15:53.651
Thank you.

01:16:57.840 --> 01:17:00.207
Good, good. You take it to the car.

01:17:02.720 --> 01:17:05.371
Here, you, take...
Take the cake. I will be five minutes.

01:17:12.800 --> 01:17:15.644
My son, it's his birthday.

01:17:15.720 --> 01:17:17.688
They were there. They knew.

01:17:17.760 --> 01:17:19.683
You shouldn't be here.

01:17:25.600 --> 01:17:28.649
Your target is an American neo-con.

01:17:29.000 --> 01:17:31.970
Head of a think-tank, instrumental
in planning the war on terror.

01:17:33.760 --> 01:17:35.569
His daughter is getting married
to an Englishman.

01:17:35.640 --> 01:17:36.801
Where?

01:17:37.280 --> 01:17:39.931
I'll know tomorrow.
You still have your phone, huh?

01:17:42.560 --> 01:17:44.050
God be with you, my friend.

01:17:50.560 --> 01:17:51.766
Will I see my family?

01:17:52.160 --> 01:17:53.286
What?

01:17:56.560 --> 01:18:00.281
Oh, you'll see everyone
who's important in your life.

01:18:01.000 --> 01:18:04.129
Everyone who has passed away,
and... And... And it will seem like

01:18:04.760 --> 01:18:07.366
only half a day has passed
since you last saw them.

01:18:09.520 --> 01:18:10.521
Huh?

01:18:38.680 --> 01:18:39.966
You OK?

01:18:40.560 --> 01:18:41.846
I'm good.

01:18:44.440 --> 01:18:45.885
You did well.

01:18:48.520 --> 01:18:49.681
Stay alert.

01:19:10.800 --> 01:19:13.246
- Yeah.

01:19:14.760 --> 01:19:16.489
Yeah, I know the place.

01:20:22.640 --> 01:20:24.722
For those of you looking for reasons,

01:20:24.800 --> 01:20:27.280
then I suggest you pay
attention to what I have to say.

01:20:28.120 --> 01:20:31.522
For far too long, you've ignored
what is happening around you.

01:20:31.600 --> 01:20:34.729
You've not seen the inevitable
that is coming at you.

01:20:34.800 --> 01:20:36.723
The inevitability of my actions.

01:21:12.640 --> 01:21:14.563
Who are you, hey?

01:21:15.560 --> 01:21:17.005
Who are you working for?

01:21:17.280 --> 01:21:19.851
- Talk to me. Who sent you?

01:21:19.920 --> 01:21:21.843
 You've never opened
your mouths in protest

01:21:21.920 --> 01:21:23.445
at my people's suffering.

01:21:23.560 --> 01:21:24.686
Answer me!

01:21:24.760 --> 01:21:27.843
- Your silence has been deafening.
- Who sent you? Talk!

01:21:27.920 --> 01:21:30.605
Words have had no impact on you.

01:21:30.680 --> 01:21:32.728
Politics has had no impact on you.

01:21:33.280 --> 01:21:36.443
Look at Afghanistan, Iraq, Palestine.
The list goes on and on.

01:21:36.520 --> 01:21:38.090
And you continue to ignore it.

01:21:43.520 --> 01:21:45.443
You seem confused at our actions.

01:21:46.360 --> 01:21:48.169
Lost in your decadent world.

01:21:48.400 --> 01:21:49.606
Unable to act.

01:21:49.920 --> 01:21:51.331
Unable to move.

01:21:51.400 --> 01:21:53.164
Frozen in time.

01:21:53.240 --> 01:21:56.642
So now I'm going to communicate to
you in a language you can understand.

01:21:57.680 --> 01:21:58.886
My words are dead

01:21:59.000 --> 01:22:01.526
until I give them life with
your blood and mine.

01:22:03.640 --> 01:22:05.608
(Static over earpiece)

01:22:13.160 --> 01:22:15.925
I'm sure by now your
newspapers and television

01:22:16.000 --> 01:22:17.968
have depicted me as a madman,

01:22:18.040 --> 01:22:20.646
an evil outsider
hell-bent on destruction.

01:22:21.120 --> 01:22:23.407
Your corrupt and degenerate media

01:22:23.480 --> 01:22:26.051
will spin my actions to suit
the government agenda.

01:22:26.400 --> 01:22:29.404
They want you misinformed,
scared and docile,

01:22:29.480 --> 01:22:32.086
so that you continue to ignore
their murderous actions.

01:22:34.880 --> 01:22:37.645
They are happy for you
to lose yourself and all that this world

01:22:37.720 --> 01:22:39.768
has to offer so that you stay unaware

01:22:39.840 --> 01:22:42.764
and intoxicated
with their mindless chatter.

01:22:42.960 --> 01:22:46.407
So that you do not question
the situation you find yourselves in.

01:22:46.640 --> 01:22:49.041
Trapped in a vicious circle
of your own doing.

01:22:50.560 --> 01:22:52.642
My life has been a journey
towards violence,

01:22:52.720 --> 01:22:53.881
but it's not one I regret.

01:22:53.960 --> 01:22:56.850
There is no guilt for me.
There is no thoughts of the past

01:22:56.920 --> 01:22:59.002
or what I did or didn't do.
My search is over.

01:22:59.560 --> 01:23:00.891
My hands have been guided by

01:23:00.960 --> 01:23:03.361
a force that's greater
than anything on this world.

01:23:03.440 --> 01:23:04.885
I've found my peace.

01:23:05.640 --> 01:23:08.450
You must understand that things
do not happen without reason.

01:23:09.000 --> 01:23:11.082
There are no coincidences.

01:23:14.520 --> 01:23:16.010
Come in, come in.

01:23:16.080 --> 01:23:17.889
So listen carefully
to what I have to say.

01:23:17.960 --> 01:23:21.646
Where are you?
Give us your location, where are you?

01:23:23.440 --> 01:23:25.681
Everything is in position.
He has entered and heading towards

01:23:25.760 --> 01:23:28.684
the kitchen area.
CCTV has been immobilized.

01:23:34.000 --> 01:23:37.766
The material world that you
worship is meaningless and empty.

01:23:38.040 --> 01:23:39.724
It means nothing to me.

01:23:39.880 --> 01:23:41.370
I leave it behind gladly.

01:23:42.840 --> 01:23:45.491
- I have sacrificed myself...

01:23:45.560 --> 01:23:48.803
...for something higher than what
this world has to offer.

01:23:48.880 --> 01:23:50.609
I strive for a higher ground.

01:24:00.800 --> 01:24:02.768
Now, your government,

01:24:03.440 --> 01:24:06.489
the government that you voted for,

01:24:06.560 --> 01:24:09.484
commit atrocities against
my people all over this world.

01:24:12.680 --> 01:24:15.570
Your support for them
makes you responsible.

01:24:16.240 --> 01:24:17.366
I'm not a hypocrite.

01:24:17.440 --> 01:24:20.284
I will not sit by while my brothers
and sisters are being slaughtered.

01:25:09.720 --> 01:25:12.405
The path that has led me here
has been littered with obstacles.

01:25:12.720 --> 01:25:14.563
But I have remained strong.

01:25:14.640 --> 01:25:16.404
I am sure of my actions.

01:25:16.480 --> 01:25:17.845
Then I will not falter.

01:25:58.760 --> 01:26:02.526
Until you stop the bombing,
imprisonment and torture of my people,

01:26:03.200 --> 01:26:04.611
we will not stop.

01:26:05.920 --> 01:26:08.969
We have entered the realm of war,
and I am a soldier.

01:26:09.960 --> 01:26:13.521
Until we feel security,
you will be our targets.

01:26:13.600 --> 01:26:15.682
You are all responsible
for turning a blind eye

01:26:15.760 --> 01:26:17.524
to the butchery of my people.

01:26:22.560 --> 01:26:25.564
I'm only a man, but my actions
are the price you pay

01:26:25.640 --> 01:26:27.927
for your apathy, for your debauchery.

01:26:28.800 --> 01:26:31.849
I've lived amongst you,
but I'm not a part of you.

01:26:32.520 --> 01:26:34.409
You've not seen me until now.

01:26:34.760 --> 01:26:36.603
I am God's lonely man.

01:27:01.360 --> 01:27:04.330
Your 9/11s, your 7/7s,
are what my people

01:27:04.400 --> 01:27:06.767
suffer on a daily basis
around the world.

01:27:06.840 --> 01:27:08.683
You know nothing of suffering.

01:27:09.400 --> 01:27:11.209
So now I'm going to show you.

01:27:12.920 --> 01:27:15.161
My prayers have all been answered

01:27:15.240 --> 01:27:18.084
and no earthly force can
take them away from me.

01:27:19.040 --> 01:27:20.769
I will rise up against you.

01:27:31.040 --> 01:27:32.849
- You'll not forget me.

01:28:05.000 --> 01:28:08.049
You have killed thousands
of my brothers and sisters.

01:28:09.320 --> 01:28:12.802
That much death has a consequence
you will pay for with your blood.

01:28:19.440 --> 01:28:23.001
There will be more like me,
l promise you.

01:28:23.520 --> 01:28:26.410
And we will bring hell
to you and your kind.

01:28:32.080 --> 01:28:34.162
And my conscience is clear.

01:28:35.360 --> 01:28:36.566
I have no regrets.

01:28:38.840 --> 01:28:42.845
I live forever. I go to a better place.

01:28:57.440 --> 01:28:59.329
What the hell is going on?

01:28:59.400 --> 01:29:01.084
You'll need my car.

01:29:02.560 --> 01:29:03.641
We need my car.

01:30:17.880 --> 01:30:19.803
- Don't! Stop!
- Where's your jacket?

01:31:54.200 --> 01:31:56.248
My name is Hussein Malik.

01:31:56.320 --> 01:31:57.401
For three years I've worked

01:31:57.480 --> 01:31:59.721
as an undercover agent
for our Secret Services

01:32:00.320 --> 01:32:03.529
and infiltrated Nabil Alawi
and his circle.

01:32:04.160 --> 01:32:06.766
Three months ago,
I discovered a plot by Nabil

01:32:06.840 --> 01:32:10.083
to steal Semtex for the purposes
of an attack on London.

01:32:10.920 --> 01:32:13.491
I informed my controllers
to arrest Nabil.

01:32:13.840 --> 01:32:16.446
The following day,
the first bomb exploded.

01:32:18.160 --> 01:32:21.846
I met with my controllers.
They tried to take my life.

01:32:21.920 --> 01:32:23.888
My life is in great danger.

01:32:23.960 --> 01:32:25.689
I need a guarantee of protection.

01:32:26.360 --> 01:32:28.567
A Secret Service team
are after me now.

01:32:29.440 --> 01:32:33.604
l have enclosed the evidence I have
accumulated and proof of my identity.

01:32:50.040 --> 01:32:53.203
Since sweeping to
power last month in a landslide victory,

01:32:53.280 --> 01:32:56.443
the new government has been
quick to make domestic security

01:32:56.520 --> 01:32:58.124
the top of their agenda.

01:32:58.520 --> 01:33:01.126
Having been given a mandate by
the public with such

01:33:01.200 --> 01:33:02.850
a resounding election victory,

01:33:02.920 --> 01:33:07.164
it's our duty to follow that lead,
and to prioritize making

01:33:07.240 --> 01:33:11.290
our country absolutely safe
from these cowardly terrorists.

01:33:12.000 --> 01:33:13.604
One of the government's first steps

01:33:13.680 --> 01:33:17.651
was the removal of the Secret
Service's old guard, Sir Scott Catesby,

01:33:18.160 --> 01:33:20.481
and the passing of
more stringent terror laws

01:33:20.560 --> 01:33:23.962
which saw the deportation
of the radical cleric Nabil Alawi.

01:33:24.480 --> 01:33:28.565
I am returning to my country
of birth tomorrow

01:33:28.640 --> 01:33:31.530
but I am distraught that the country

01:33:31.600 --> 01:33:35.491
that is my home is expelling me
on false charges.

01:33:36.120 --> 01:33:40.170
I will fight for my corner.
God save the Queen.

01:33:41.120 --> 01:33:42.770
Last week also saw

01:33:42.840 --> 01:33:45.047
the first official announcement
into the bombings.

01:33:45.640 --> 01:33:48.291
The perpetrators
were a home-grown cell.

01:33:49.280 --> 01:33:53.444
None had been identified as
potential threats prior to the attacks.

01:33:54.560 --> 01:33:57.530
Meaning they were all cleanskins,

01:33:57.840 --> 01:34:00.446
completely unknown to any
of the intelligence services.

01:34:01.720 --> 01:34:03.609
The ringleader,Ashraf Ahmed,

01:34:03.680 --> 01:34:07.082
was personally responsible for
the bombing of the Glassmore Hotel.

01:34:07.440 --> 01:34:10.444
The bomb was a timed device
placed in a luggage item,

01:34:10.600 --> 01:34:13.410
causing a massive explosion
in the foyer of the hotel.

01:34:13.840 --> 01:34:16.525
Ahmed himself was
killed by security services

01:34:16.600 --> 01:34:21.208
as he tried to trigger a suicide device
just prior to the foyer device exploding.

01:34:21.600 --> 01:34:24.604
Helen James, head of the
Glassmore Hotel Victims Committee,

01:34:24.680 --> 01:34:27.047
had this to say about the findings.

01:34:27.120 --> 01:34:29.964
I don't see how you solve
the underlying problem

01:34:30.040 --> 01:34:34.170
and I don't think anyone really does.
And, of course, this may lead to...

01:34:34.360 --> 01:34:38.285
to, you know, more security
and more troops going out

01:34:38.360 --> 01:34:40.362
and possibly more people being killed,

01:34:40.440 --> 01:34:42.090
but I don't see how
that solves the problem.

01:34:56.600 --> 01:35:00.161
Ewan! I thought they'd gotten to you.

01:35:16.320 --> 01:35:17.367
There you go.

01:35:51.720 --> 01:35:53.768
It was with his files.

01:35:55.560 --> 01:35:57.562
You must have left it
when you last met.

01:36:00.520 --> 01:36:02.363
You knew all about the bombings.

01:36:03.640 --> 01:36:05.324
Pretended you were
trying to stop them.

01:36:06.640 --> 01:36:08.881
You worked with this Nabil,

01:36:08.960 --> 01:36:12.009
then got him safely deported
without arrest.

01:36:12.080 --> 01:36:14.082
And I wasn't meant to make it out alive.

01:36:14.920 --> 01:36:17.446
You were in line with
a promotion of the new government,

01:36:17.800 --> 01:36:20.531
helped them win, got rid of your boss.
Must be happy with you.

01:36:24.080 --> 01:36:25.809
Played me perfectly.

01:36:28.120 --> 01:36:29.849
Knew all about my wife.

01:36:32.280 --> 01:36:34.521
Knew I'd kill anyone you put
in front of me.

01:36:36.520 --> 01:36:38.761
You can use her
as an excuse if you want.

01:36:39.640 --> 01:36:44.009
But what you do is in your nature.

01:36:50.640 --> 01:36:55.282
I love my country.
I'd kill for it and I'd die for it.

01:36:56.960 --> 01:36:58.405
Good for you.

01:37:01.840 --> 01:37:04.047
The press have been sent
copies of these files.

01:37:04.120 --> 01:37:05.884
They show you were responsible.

01:37:05.960 --> 01:37:07.849
Those files are nonsense you made up.

01:37:07.920 --> 01:37:09.763
No one will believe it.

01:37:09.840 --> 01:37:11.205
They might...

01:37:13.400 --> 01:37:16.449
if you buckle under
the pressure of the story.

01:37:23.360 --> 01:37:25.249
You're out of your mind.

01:37:26.440 --> 01:37:27.965
It's in my nature.

